.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇人跌番規？"},{"pid":"bb6f057053ef8a75cd7499fc8053ddc8274b8cac","tid":14592,"uid":14173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會傾政治野<br />\n觀念係咪好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會 其實週不時都會傾下<br />\n觀念唔會好唔同 宜家後生既其實好理性<br />\n我仲會同佢地分享下雨傘運動時候既事同相</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打識d人好 我係NYC 試過同大陸人講政治 真係會嘈交 本身都知大家政治觀念唔同 都唔會點講 佢自己冇啦啦拎出黎講 我先同佢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有睇人既 有啲牛皮燈籠點唔著就唔洗同佢講太多<br />\n但我識個班就好好 都好有興趣知香港既政治野"},{"pid":"94f7f1590b723f4040450934c1699681bf2f6924","tid":14592,"uid":14173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沖涼房有冇分開一格格？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇人跌番規？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用洗頭水 沐浴露<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7335354f904ec2996c35a17872b5bd8f4d35d06b","tid":14592,"uid":14173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學讀啲咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n文化野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba6e04b4a66c9f657384853cd4e2348929b13b8","tid":14592,"uid":14173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌左幾多個大陸妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一兩個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf1c137c4f3ae267715ff9416aecf068b07b5e1","tid":14592,"uid":6197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌左幾多個大陸妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" cla